  "text": "Patients with gastrointestinal and lung cancers whose weight stabilized while on chemotherapy had significantly better PFS and OS than patients exhibiting continued weight loss [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Hence, does weight loss during chemotherapy influence the outcomes in patients with advanced GC? Exactly how much weight loss is too much?",
